  | doi = 
  | id = 
  | isbn =9781932792041
  | page = 224 }}</ref> The college archives were created in 1963 and the first history of the college, spanning from 1900 to 1950, was published by [[James R. Cameron]] in 1968.<ref name="history">{{cite news 
  | last = Davis
  | first = Joy
