  | title = Eastern Nazarene College Catalogue 2007-2008, p. 9
  | work = 
  | publisher = 
  | date = 
  | url = http://www.enc.edu/downloads/undergrad_catalog_07-08.pdf
  |format=PDF| doi = 
  | accessdate = 2008-07-10 |archiveurl = http://web.archive.org/web/20080627054257/http://www.enc.edu/downloads/undergrad_catalog_07-08.pdf <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2008-06-27}}</ref> ENC gained [[Educational accreditation|institutional accreditation]] from the Commission on Institutions of Higher Education of the [[New England Association of Schools and Colleges]] (NEASC)<ref>{{cite web
  | last = 
