====Athletics====
[[Intramural]] sports take place year-round and change from season to season based on student interest (past sports have included [[lacrosse]], [[field hockey]], and a very successful men's volleyball club).<ref>{{cite news 
  | last = Fine
  | first = Mike
  | coauthors = 
  | title = Going for the Kill: ENC's undefeated volleyball team continues its winning tradition
