Lawrence Yerdon is the president of the [[Strawbery Banke]] Museum in [[Portsmouth, New Hampshire]]. He also served 1986-2004 as president of the [[Hancock Shaker Village]] in [[Pittsfield, Massachusetts]] and was director of the [[Quincy Historical Society]] 1976-1986.<ref>{{cite news 
  | last = Kittredge
  | first = Claire
  | coauthors = 
