[[John S. Rigden]] is an alumnus and world-renowned physicist. [[Eldon C. Hall]] was the lead design engineer of the [[Apollo Guidance Computer]] (AGC) at MIT. Ross Tubo is Vice President of Stem Cell and Chemokine Biology at [[Genzyme]].<ref>{{cite web
  | last = 
